{"tid":1059083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV界金鐘獎名單出爐　22歲正妹奪女優獎","createTime":"2019-03-13T02:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T04:46:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3cab657c7fa8e80a3996f4937e4704985359717a","tid":1059083,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9QeorK_FRPw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9QeorK_FRPw&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=43c7f9e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9QeorK_FRPw</a><br />\n<br />\n日本AV界盛事，2019成人廣播獎於3月12日公布得獎名單，「女優賞」為戶田真琴、「新人女優賞」唯井真尋(唯井まひろ)、「熟女女優賞」為加藤綾野(加藤あやの)<br />\n <br />\n據《東京sports》報導，3月12日在東京舉行2019年成人廣播獎頒獎典禮，獲得女優賞的戶田真琴表示，「有著『如果沒獲獎的話怎麼辦才好』這樣不安的心情，不過大家都對我說沒問題的，讓我真的很開心跟感動，我想成為第一，今後將會持續向前，不會停止」。<br />\n <br />\n新人女優賞的唯井真尋說「講真的，我現在淚流滿面，我真的很開心，開心的笑了，出的汗說不定會讓隱形胸罩給弄掉了！」。熟女女優賞的加藤綾野指出，「不知道該怎麼表達現在的心情，很感謝大家的支持，也感謝投票的人，無法用言語說出我的感謝之情」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHxac4J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHxac4J.png&h=ff0159bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDChCwp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDChCwp.png&h=5cf2f340&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GtchCwr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtchCwr.png&h=ccfbba32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E4KzEKN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE4KzEKN.png&h=6fc63a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5wutC9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5wutC9.png&h=99aea1ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd23a6e99efb553aca7ceb3f4f24bc859232944e","tid":1059083,"uid":16846,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"開始唔識啲名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p